{"tid":1633990,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大戰當前，談何收手？","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:55:21.000Z","uid":198822,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b10f19106c6866178527ae3b29e56d9f3752ad40","tid":1633990,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"暴政動用緊急法三天後，不少人突然叫「勇武休息，和理非接力」，如果和理非接到力，昨天港島出現三百萬人遊行，根本不會有眾多勇武前線被捕。<br />\n<br />\n大戰在前，突然叫停勇武的客觀效果是助長了暴政的氣焰，以為動用緊急法成功嚇退勇武，並且分化了和理非及勇武，打散四個多月來「不分化不割席」的共識。"},{"pid":"5733fb57ca8e536d4d28af0f67867e039c5c20a0","tid":1633990,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"8ef940ba42def0feeeb44bd91f6c4a283d340a0d","tid":1633990,"uid":78732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1rTwP8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1rTwP8.png&h=7db13fe1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dda81b0ecdcc4c7dcb2e976c1560c9cb7fe3bbdb","tid":1633990,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aec9b1b64d23da9e6902c21238bbcce163917531","tid":1633990,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e4fee16948f3025bbfa21d095c497d482464f1","tid":1633990,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Msvy6j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Msvy6j.jpg&h=648f7f42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd1b38969d6491134e4a1e051a37a250027f4d1c","tid":1633990,"uid":315038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"//突然叫停勇武的客觀效果是助長了暴政的氣焰，以為動用緊急法成功嚇退勇武，並且分化了和理非及勇武，打散四個多月來「不分化不割席」的共識。//<br />\n<br />\n繼續裝修就真係「打散四個多月來「不分化不割席」的共識」喇！<br />\n我身邊啲人(老人家)已經喺度嘈我點解要支持裝修嘅人<br />\n我一直以來花咗唔知幾多口水先至令啲老人家支持我地，而家畀啲裝修佬一鋪清袋"},{"pid":"10b3c51f3c3da0ae90112db959fb681e89ece158","tid":1633990,"uid":135697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd1c5bb69d71ad1129b4fb83d9e49fd4f7e78325","tid":1633990,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4344426a560f5613824bdb6b41ddd688a7403671","tid":1633990,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:30:12.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"95e8b7d817f72515f2fa58da9ec3a8b3218fa820","tid":1633990,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79a376bfea29505081732bca883127ecb18292c","tid":1633990,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"勇武收檔就差唔多"},{"pid":"6d067d0839b4f0f8f6e9bb27aafb639b50789d49","tid":1633990,"uid":150083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"今晚8點遍地開花"},{"pid":"fbee38ca2f92e7f59cdd43211cdb75d0cc1b898c","tid":1633990,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你就搞分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分和勇be water嘅精隨係每個人都可以係和勇 能收能放 需要時勇武 需要時和理 雖然現實依種模式唔可以完全理想地進行<br />\n<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔係你口中咁 分開兩班人</span> 係意識形態上就分開兩種人 分成兩種理念不同嘅人 再引發對立嘅言論 分化兩班人"},{"pid":"fd40bca7e69a856a72e9bbe80d0d3665aef3c006","tid":1633990,"uid":150083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"今晚8點遍地開花"},{"pid":"3e8dbb5007593324d26210849f1e4aead4808dae","tid":1633990,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"大家要記住 兄弟爬山 各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1bc73707c93db01a5489d2012c23abb85ea45f","tid":1633990,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:53:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">( Show Blocked User - Frizzle(港豬) )</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ff049a5f26ecf8807be9bda013de3916ac81dab0","tid":1633990,"uid":204095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}